lead_paragraph: One year later, the New York Mets finally landed All-Star outfielder Jay Bruce to boost a struggling lineup. And now, he'll provide protection for Yoenis Cespedes rather than an alternative to him.

headline.print_headline: Mets Acquire NL RBI Leader Jay Bruce From Reds
